Description: Implements methods for RCON models for paired data, including an Alternating Direction Method of Multipliers (ADMM) algorithm for solving the penalized likelihood problem introduced by Ranciati and Roverato (2024). Provides functions for computing maximum likelihood estimates and for generating simulated pdRCON models and datasets.
